Welcome to the Lightning Shell! Read more at https://lightningshell.app

Recently added apps: "btc2fiat" (show Bitcoin price), "sc-im" (spreadsheet), "csview" (view CSV files), "links" (web browser), "perfectly-balanced" (LND node balancing).

Use the /data directory to store files that you don't want to lose (configuration files, custom scripts, etc.)

Run "about" for more details about Lightning Shell.
Run "man apps" to read about all available apps.
